msgid ""
"Prime {scope}:\n"
"  • {names}\n"
"\n"
"Each mapping is primed with the options set in its own configuration (the "
"trash field): additive mappings upload without ever deleting; mirror "
"mappings (trash / permanent) reconcile the destination. Once done, the "
"mappings become available for real-time processing.\n"
"\n"
"The real-time consumer and the scheduled timer are paused during priming and "
"restored afterwards. This can take a while on large folders (it is "
"interruptible and resumes where it left off).\n"
"\n"
"Start priming?"
msgstr ""
"Inicializar {scope}:\n"
"  • {names}\n"
"\n"
"Cada asignación se inicializa con las opciones definidas en su propia "
"configuración (el campo papelera): las asignaciones aditivas suben sin "
"eliminar nunca; las asignaciones espejo (papelera / permanente) reconcilian "
"el destino. Una vez hecho, las asignaciones quedan disponibles para el "
"procesamiento en tiempo real.\n"
"\n"
"El consumidor en tiempo real y el temporizador programado se pausan durante "
"la inicialización y se restauran después. Puede tardar un rato en carpetas "
"grandes (es interrumpible y se reanuda donde se quedó).\n"
"\n"
"¿Iniciar la inicialización?"

